section.def:
current
                (電流) means an electric current exceeding
            one-thousandth part of one ampere;

generator
                (發電機) means the dynamo or dynamos or other
            electrical apparatus used for the generation of energy;

motor
                (發動機) means any electric motor carried on a car
            and used for the conversion of energy;

pipe
                (喉管) means any gas or water pipe, or other
            metallic pipe, structure or substance;
